---

<section
    id="positive-trade"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10"
>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <span
                class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4 trigo-positive-chapter"
                >El Comercio</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-6">El Primer Dinero</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#a8a29e] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Antes del oro, fue el grano. El siclo (shekel) original no era una moneda, era una
                medida de peso de cebada.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-12">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <p class="text-base text-[#d6d3d1] leading-relaxed">
                    El excedente de trigo permitió el comercio a larga distancia. Conectó tribus
                    aisladas. Llevó obsidiana de Anatolia a Jericó y conchas del Mediterráneo al
                    desierto.
                </p>
                <p class="text-base text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                    El trigo tejió la primera red global de cooperación humana. No solo alimentó
                    cuerpos, sino que creó las primeras rutas comerciales que unirían
                    civilizaciones.
                </p>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-4">
                    <div
                        class="text-center p-4 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20"
                    >
                        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-1">1 Siclo</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">
                            ≈ 180 granos
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="text-center p-4 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20"
                    >
                        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-1">3000km</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">
                            Rutas comerciales
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-900/10 via-transparent to-transparent"
                >
                </div>

                <div class="relative w-full max-w-[400px]">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" class="w-full h-full">
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="tradeGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                                <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#10b981;stop-opacity:0.3"
                                ></stop>
                                <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#059669;stop-opacity:0.6"
                                ></stop>
                            </linearGradient>
                        </defs>

                        <!-- Central hub -->
                        <circle
                            cx="200"
                            cy="200"
                            r="40"
                            fill="url(#tradeGradient)"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="r"
                                values="40;45;40"
                                dur="3s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </circle>
                        <text
                            x="200"
                            y="205"
                            text-anchor="middle"
                            fill="#10b981"
                            font-size="14"
                            font-weight="bold">TRIGO</text
                        >

                        <!-- Trade nodes -->
                        <!-- Node 1: Top -->
                        <circle
                            cx="200"
                            cy="80"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="200" y="85" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Anatolia</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="200"
                            y1="160"
                            x2="200"
                            y2="105"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="1s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>

                        <!-- Node 2: Top Right -->
                        <circle
                            cx="320"
                            cy="120"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="320" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Jericó</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="230"
                            y1="175"
                            x2="295"
                            y2="135"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="1.2s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>

                        <!-- Node 3: Right -->
                        <circle
                            cx="340"
                            cy="200"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="340" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Uruk</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="240"
                            y1="200"
                            x2="315"
                            y2="200"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="1.5s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>

                        <!-- Node 4: Bottom Right -->
                        <circle
                            cx="320"
                            cy="280"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="320" y="285" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Egipto</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="230"
                            y1="225"
                            x2="295"
                            y2="265"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="1.8s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>

                        <!-- Node 5: Bottom -->
                        <circle
                            cx="200"
                            cy="320"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="200" y="325" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Sumeria</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="200"
                            y1="240"
                            x2="200"
                            y2="295"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="2s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>

                        <!-- Node 6: Bottom Left -->
                        <circle
                            cx="80"
                            cy="280"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="80" y="285" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Levante</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="170"
                            y1="225"
                            x2="105"
                            y2="265"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="1.3s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>

                        <!-- Node 7: Left -->
                        <circle
                            cx="60"
                            cy="200"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="60" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Creta</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="160"
                            y1="200"
                            x2="85"
                            y2="200"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="1.7s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>

                        <!-- Node 8: Top Left -->
                        <circle
                            cx="80"
                            cy="120"
                            r="25"
                            fill="#1c1917"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.8"></circle>
                        <text x="80" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8a29e" font-size="10"
                            >Chipre</text
                        >
                        <line
                            x1="170"
                            y1="175"
                            x2="105"
                            y2="135"
                            stroke="#10b981"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-dasharray="5,5"
                            opacity="0.5"
                        >
                            <animate
                                attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
                                from="0"
                                to="10"
                                dur="1.4s"
                                repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                        </line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div
                class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] p-6 rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all group"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-emerald-900/50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e7e5e4]">Obsidiana</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e]">De Anatolia a Mesopotamia</p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] p-6 rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all group"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-emerald-900/50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.456 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e7e5e4]">Lapislázuli</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e]">De Afganistán al Mediterráneo</p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] p-6 rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all group"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-emerald-900/50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 01-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 014.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0112 15a9.065 9.065 0 00-6.23-.693L5 14.5m14.8.8l1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0112 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e7e5e4]">Conchas</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e]">Del Mediterráneo al desierto</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
